{"tid":1269972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家唔係同佢哋鬥短命，係鬥長命","createTime":"2019-06-30T17:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T01:10:58.000Z","uid":64601,"like":280,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"8c4e4a99cd1e29c68181c7480b4aee101389579b","tid":1269972,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"我哋最大嘅本錢係青春，你睇下今日撐警遊行嘅年齡層幾大，人數幾少，我哋手上嘅一票，就係激撚死嗰班建制狗最強武器。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你有諗過輕生或者半隻腳企緊出去嘅，希望你同香港人一齊拖住手行埋落去，你手上正正係掌握香港未來嘅一票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知最近好多負面新聞，你好嬲你好無助，但正正係你咁憎上一代嘅敗懷，你更加唔可以早死過佢哋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我哋處於夾心階層，四十歲打上多數藍，00後中學生到三十幾歲多數係真正為香港未來企出嚟嘅人，而小學嘅就係俾佢哋四十歲老豆老母洗腦、成日講普通話嘅一輩，所以我哋更加要負起責任，教育好下一代。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以當為咗香港未來，可唔可以繼續一齊奮鬥落去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a8f36090281ea8df2eb77778b17a822272257a","tid":1269972,"uid":48,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:24:06.000Z","msg":"100/10"},{"pid":"bdf39ae8f0b4ff287ec0002b3bf5300fd5567868","tid":1269972,"uid":164987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7909ce018ce04dd26db1758cf25655644c1b029e","tid":1269972,"uid":32753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"100000/.1"},{"pid":"9f381a2603f5bab953a08bb4c41d346c76bebede","tid":1269972,"uid":211727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:24:56.000Z","msg":